Description.LocalizedString: A manifestation of guilt, this punishing force took shape in the nightmares of the tormented.
Born from the unhinged minds of his victims tormented by guilt.
A massive chef's knife to reap affliction and misery from his victims.
Caring and impulsive, Cheryl Mason, previously known as Heather, attempted to rebuild her life after the tragic death of her adoptive father, Harry Mason.
A warm vest to keep her from harm at night with a broken flashlight that she kept as a good luck charm.
Fashionable skirt and warm boots to face what lurks in the dark.
A manifestation of guilt, this punishing force took shape in Cheryl's dreams and tormented her with nightmarish visions of gore.
Born from the unhinged minds of his victims that he tormented with brutal and sanguinary methods.
A massive, bloodstained chef's knife to reap affliction and misery from his victims.
